We are seeking Enrolled Nurse to join our growing group of specialists.
The job scope includes:
• Provide Nursing care to patients.
• Answer to patient's queries.
• Dispensing of medication.
• Perform basic triage.
• Assist in minor procedures.
• Provide frontline customer service.
• Scheduling of appointment and patient registration.
• Handling invoice and payment collection.
• Process invoice and payment collection.
• Booking of referral appointments
• Maintaining inventory levels and Quarterly stoke take.
• Handle administrative and ad-hoc duties.
Job Requirements:
• Diploma in Nursing
• Required language(s): English, Mandarin (to liaise with our Chinese patients)
• At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for the position.
• Required Skill(s): Microsoft Office.
• Preferably Entry Level specialized in Health care - Nurse/Medical Support &amp; Assistant or equivalent.
• Experience in O&amp;G, Dermatology or Paediatrics will be an advantage.
Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
